'I see that you have gained proficiency as an expert cook! That is excellent, [placeholder]. You are showing remarkable progress.

'You are about ready to learn to be an artisan cook, which is the next step along your path to mastery. To do this, though, you will need to prove your worth to the expert cook in Michel Delving.

'If you impress Jewel Underhill, she may allow you to use the superior oven to create delectable foods from your artisan recipes. Not many have this honour!'
